Package: SPRthis
Title: Automate package and project setup for systemPipeR Workflow packages
Version: 0.9.0
Date: 2021-02-05
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Daniela", family = "Cassol", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="danielac@ucr.edu"))
Description: This package expends biocthis and usethis packages, providing automation to create systemPipeR workflows templates.
biocViews: Infrastructure
Imports: systemPipeR (>= 1.24.0), systemPipeRdata (>= 1.18.0)
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: SPRthis can be used to run external 
        command-line software, but the corresponding tool needs to be installed on a system.  
License: Artistic-2.0
URL: https://github.com/dcassol/SPRthis
